{"tid":334402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［開戰］美偵察機東海上空遭兩殲十攔截敗走","createTime":"2017-07-24T15:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T16:34:54.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb184d9d186e3fb9e74e4949e5c365066abc829","tid":334402,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:49:12.000Z","msg":"美軍一架EP3偵察機，周日（23日）下午逼近中國航母遼寧號母港所在地山東青島。解放軍兩架殲10戰機攜帶空對空導彈緊急升空，在距青島150公里的黃海上空近距離攔截美軍偵察機。雙方幾乎相撞，迫使美機離開。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒引述兩名華府官員指，解放軍戰機當時掛有導彈，「危險並故意地」逼近偵察機。其中一架位於偵察機下方的殲10，突然採取戰術動作，向上爬升90米，幾乎與偵察機相撞。官員指，美方偵察機被迫採取緊急迴避動作，而國防部已就解放軍戰鬥機的「不專業」行為展開調查。 <br />\n<br />\n今次是5月下旬中美軍機在香港附近空域狹路相逢後，雙方再度危險遭遇。山東青島是北海艦隊司令部所在地，為中國首艘航母遼寧號的母港，而中國的核潛艇基地亦在黃海附近，疑美軍偵察機是為偵察上述軍事目標而來。遼寧號早前訪港後，穿越台海返回青島，據指美軍曾派出軍艦、潛艇跟蹤偵察。 <br />\n<br />\nEP3可用於偵察各種電子通訊信號。2001年海南島對開發生中美軍機相撞事件，被撞擊後緊急降落的美方軍機，就是一架EP3。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170724/mobile/bkncn-20170724220143420-0724_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170724%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20170724220143420-0724_05011_001.html&d=nEwcrg5US3u%2FgtZee83eAUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6760d58c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170724/mobile/bkncn-20170724220143420-0724_05011_001.html</a><br />\n中共真大膽"},{"pid":"07c908fddaf5f6c9bd546e167f8a6eb8506def45","tid":334402,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"做乜唔射9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a7515bb57e70289166fcc4c17a997da245205b","tid":334402,"uid":98172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:03:34.000Z","msg":"又係白粉, 閱"},{"pid":"b700ee1dadb0d76077f2a11df9f6c5a46dc054a1","tid":334402,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:07:15.000Z","msg":"今次是5月下旬中美軍機在香港附近空域狹路相逢後，雙方再度危險遭遇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e80c2697ffc7b68ebef62aa889723a57d2c37e","tid":334402,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/000725_92a991e11d6f259c6128b8ecf319d166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F000725_92a991e11d6f259c6128b8ecf319d166.jpg&h=12bb8713&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67609549c475cebdde2900f1f55adcb8ea77edde","tid":334402,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"人地偵察完咪走囉, <br />\n唔通無限期滯空？<br />\n<br />\n同秀姑話自己屌走神駒有何分別?"},{"pid":"de0af466dd66bb67c08197c968695eb1c63fc5aa","tid":334402,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"遲早擦槍走火"},{"pid":"c2bc6be43e616475bfaf2122259ae6c34638ecac","tid":334402,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41439dfdeb98fc9ebe608faffa06754b541ec7c2","tid":334402,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲早擦槍走火</blockquote><br />\n走咩火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電子干擾仲好玩"},{"pid":"36be5a9cb533bb13a64f6378a32d413296ea0d5f","tid":334402,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遲早擦槍走火</blockquote><br />\n走咩火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電子干擾仲好玩</blockquote><br />\n口交部最多咪又咀炮"},{"pid":"3a4b9e137b1989fa1ca7a7f6aad5ee842321a7d4","tid":334402,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美帝咪又係紙老虎</blockquote><br